                ]
            ]
        },
        {
            "block_label": "text",
            "block_content": "Visual reasoning results. We further provide some qualitative visual reasoning examples of the LLaVA-13B (Liu et al., 2023a) model in Figure 6. AWQ improves the responses compared to round-to-nearest (RTN) for INT4-g128 quantization, leading to more reasonable answers. In this first example, the AWQ model can understand the meme as it resembles the Earth when looking from space, while RTN produces wrong descriptions (marked in red).",
