            "block_content": "<div style=\"text-align: center;\">Table 9. Our method is orthogonal to GPTQ: it further closes the performance gap under extreme low-bit quantization (INT2-g64) when combined with GPTQ. Results are WikiText-2 perplexity of OPT models.</div>\n",
